LevitateOS License Information
===============================

This project contains multiple components with different licenses:


1. LEVITATE BUILD TOOL (src/*)
------------------------------
License: MIT
Copyright (c) 2024-2026 LevitateOS Contributors

The Rust build tool source code in this repository is licensed under MIT.
See LICENSES/MIT.txt for the full license text.


2. BUILT ARTIFACTS
------------------
When you run `cargo run -- build all`, the resulting artifacts contain
software under different licenses:

  - Linux kernel (linux/)     : GPL-2.0-only
  - BusyBox (toolchain/)      : GPL-2.0-or-later
  - OpenRC (toolchain/)       : BSD-2-Clause
  - musl libc                 : MIT

The GPL-licensed components (Linux, BusyBox) require that source code
be made available when distributing binaries. This repository satisfies
that requirement by building everything from source.


3. DISTRIBUTION NOTICE
----------------------
If you distribute initramfs/ISO images built by this tool, you must:

  a) Include this LICENSE file or equivalent notices
  b) Provide access to source code for GPL components (Linux, BusyBox)
  c) Preserve copyright notices in BSD/MIT components

The source code for all components is available:
  - Linux:   https://kernel.org (or the linux/ submodule)
  - BusyBox: https://busybox.net
  - OpenRC:  https://github.com/OpenRC/openrc
  - musl:    https://musl.libc.org


4. FULL LICENSE TEXTS
---------------------
See the LICENSES/ directory for complete license texts:
  - LICENSES/MIT.txt           (levitate build tool, musl)
  - LICENSES/GPL-2.0.txt       (Linux, BusyBox)
  - LICENSES/BSD-2-Clause.txt  (OpenRC)
